- Serialization (not deserialization)
- Type handling
- Mixins
- Filters
- Property configuration

The buggy code path requires:
- `p.getValueAsString()` returning non-null/non-empty text
- `_deserialize(text, ctxt)` succeeding (not throwing exception)
- The logic around the null check

